node.text: Hello everyone! Let’s develop your #imagination and imagine that all objects and abstract things are humans, and live in our world! This way, you’ll be able to explain so many things that happen suddenly. Check out this video with annoying things and #relatable situations, and share what happened to you too! If you feel like you never leave the kitchen without checking your fridge, just letting you know that your fridge is such a charmer, and it’s impossible to pass him by without getting a snack ;) If your kid is playing with Legos, be careful! Many angry small pieces are on the floor waiting for you to step on them so they can hurt your feet! 😓 If today your skin looks perfect, and on the following day, all of a sudden you see #pimples on your face, just know, they wanted to hang out and have a great time, that’s why they are there😅 Keep watching to see more #fun situations that have no doubt happened to you too ;

node.title: IF ANNOYING THINGS WERE HUMANS || Useful Ideas and Hacks
